{"tid":1599834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人貼一張八達通退卡相","createTime":"2019-09-28T08:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T09:05:35.000Z","uid":144833,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd354c7509ce680d6f57807c526d485ebc73d854","tid":1599834,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"如題 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人退一張八達通 </span></strong><br />\n貼張退卡相叫埋身邊朋友退<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWDUyUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWDUyUJ.jpg&h=541595ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前見到有巴打呼籲大家退八達通<br />\n但好似無咩人真係有take action<br />\n最多都係罷用<br />\n<br />\n我唔識可以點樣帶起呢個風氣<br />\n唯有以身作則<br />\n去退咗張八達通<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vs6fimG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVs6fimG.jpg&h=6dba699b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記得塗走啲時間 卡號 剩餘金額 唔好自爆<br />\n<br />\n車船津貼？朝早3折？<br />\n唔係到呢刻仲在乎呢啲小恩小惠掛<br />\n中學生我就無意見 畢竟未有工作能力<br />\n又未必可以日日搭巴士返學 可以理解佢地嘅妥協<br />\n但係成年人就唔該有返啲堅持<br />\n<br />\n退八達通保平安<br />\n<br />\nPS 要出活動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JttDn1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JttDn1.jpg&h=26fb17cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kAWNgm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kAWNgm.jpg&h=838129cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aOA2PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aOA2PH.jpg&h=e071f2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oi5vRH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foi5vRH2.jpg&h=83cf257f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nU2BNgo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnU2BNgo.jpg&h=c1d18bcf&s={SIZE}\